Package appointment_data

Class Appointment

java.lang.Object
appointment_data.Appointment
public class Appointment extends Object
Represents an appointment in the hospital system. Provides details about the patient, doctor, date, time, status, and other appointment-related information.
Version:
1.0
Author:
WU CHENGRUI, TANG RUIXUAN

  • Constructor Details

    • Appointment

      public Appointment(String Patient, String Doctor, String Date, String Time, String status, String diagnosis, String treatments, String prescription, String medicine_status, String quantity, String note)
      Constructs an Appointment object with all relevant details.
      Parameters:
      Patient - The name of the patient.
      Doctor - The name of the doctor.
      Date - The date of the appointment.
      Time - The time of the appointment.
      status - The status of the appointment (e.g., Booked, Confirmed, Completed).
      diagnosis - The diagnosis provided during the appointment.
      treatments - The treatments recommended or performed during the appointment.
      prescription - The prescription details provided to the patient.
      medicine_status - The status of the prescribed medicine.
      quantity - The quantity of the prescribed medicine.
      note - Additional notes related to the appointment.
